    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "A new species of frogfish of the genus Histiophryne (Teleostei: Lophiiformes: Antennariidae) from Queensland, Australia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277962>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277964>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277965> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277962>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A) Histiophryne maggiewalker, new species, holotype, QM I. 38176, 55 mm SL, showing some dehydration, and B) Histiophryne maggiewalker, paratype, QM I. 37621, 60.1 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277964>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. The illicium of Histiophryne maggiewalker, QM I. 38176, 55 mm SL, and H. bougainvilli, AMS I. 17304 - 001, 58.9 mm SL." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277964/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277965>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. 50 % majority rule phylogeny for all described species of Histiophryne, from trees sampled in the posterior, generated from Bayesian analyses on a partitioned dataset that included the nuclear recombination activating gene 2 (RAG 2) and mitochondrial cytochrome oxidase-I (COI) gene." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277965/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

